      "rationale": "Primary QoI in both validation and COU is the normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and relative hemolysis index (RH). Shear stress exposure history integrated via power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied identically in validation and COU simulations. No surrogate QoIs substituted."
    },
    {
