      "rationale": "Validation performed on the identical FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. Operating conditions span the COU envelope (2.5–6.0 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Blood analog fluid (glycerol-water) used in experiments; Carreau-Yasuda model calibrated to whole blood rheology. Physiological relevance of validation activities to CPB COU assessed as high."
