      "rationale": "Formal model form assessment not required at MRL 2. SST k-omega turbulence model selection justified by literature consensus for internal rotating flow hemolysis prediction. Power-law hemolysis damage model selection consistent with FDA guidance. Qualitative justification provided; no structured model form factor assessment performed."
    },
    {
